                title: "",
                entryContent: "<p class=\"paragraph\"><!--5. -->CUSTOMIZE EVERYTHING.</p><p class=\"paragraph\">Whether you'd like to tie the knot in Mexico or Jamaica, Palace Resorts will make sure that your wedding ceremony feels uniquely you, down to the smallest linen-wrapped detail. You'll handpick everything from the flowers and reception decor to the entertainment, food, and photography. Palace Resorts also offers a range of enhancements, from horse-drawn carriages, dazzling fireworks, seaside gazebos, and spa treatments, to religious and cultural offerings.</p><p class=\"paragraph\"><!--6. -->EXPERIENCE IT ALL BEFORE YOUR WEDDING DAY.</p><p class=\"paragraph\">Considering a destination wedding at a Palace Resorts? Now it's time to experience all offerings before you get married. Enjoy a free two-night stay in Jamaica or a property in Mexico and see exactly how your dream destination wedding will come to life. During your visit, you’ll meet with specialist and suppliers, check out wedding locations, explore decor options, and sample cuisine and cake.",
